      <div class="hero section">
        <div class="section__content">
          <div class="hero__text">
            <h1>Welcome to ADK-Linux.</h1>

            <p>
            ADK-Linux is a Linux distro created with a simple plasma theme.<br>
            </p>

            <div class="hero__buttons">
              <a class="btn btn--download" href="https://github.com/Technopig100/adk-linux.git">
